## How to Update This File
At the end of each session, the executing agent:
Moves "Active Right Now" to the top of the sessions table (newest first)
Fills in Date, Agent(s), Task, Outcome, Next Step
Drops the oldest row if there are already 5 entries
Writes a new "Active Right Now" section if a task is still in progress